      "value": " \n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO9410\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601252226/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601252226&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO9410</a></p> \n<p>One side of this 8-foot-long scarf is reinforced with chain links and metal plates. While not enough to provide a benefit to <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">Armor Class</a>, these versatile scarves can be used like a length of chain to climb short distances or bind an enemy. A reinforced scarf has <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/damaging-objects#TOC-Hardness\">hardness</a> 10 and 4 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Hit-Points\">hit points</a>. It can be burst with a DC 24 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Strength</a> check.</p> \n"
